description: Returns the number of reserved minutes used by account.

parameters.name: month
parameters.description: The month being requested, with a value of 1-12.

parameters.name: year
parameters.description: The year being requested, in the format of YYYY.

nested_items.name: estimatedMinutesRemaining
nested_items.description: Estimated number of minutes remaining for an account, specific to the month being requested.

nested_items.name: isReservedMinutesCustomer
nested_items.description: Returns whether or not an account has signed up for the reserved minutes pricing plan, specific to the month being requested.

nested_items.name: totalReservedMinuteAllocation
nested_items.description: Total number of reserved minutes allocated, specific to the month being requested.

nested_items.name: totalScheduledMinutes
nested_items.description: Total scheduled minutes for an account, specific to the month being requested.

nested_items.name: upcomingMinutesScheduled
nested_items.description: Upcoming minutes scheduled for an account, specific to the month being requested.
